               <p>I am clerk of St. Catherine-Cree church. (He produced the church register of the second marriage, which was read. The letter from the first wife, dated 30th of June, was likewise read.)</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I leave my defence to my counsel. I am innocent of what I am charged with.</p>
               <p>
